      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97\u2728 I\u2019m honestly a little sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy it! This car is in absolutely incredible shape\u2014it\u2019s been babied since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no dents, and that interior? Still smells like a brand-new car! It drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for perfection without the brand-new price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin!",
