      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, a masterpiece of atmospheric engineering with individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is mechanically flawless, with the high-pressure VANOS system overhauled and rod bearings replaced as preventative measures. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual transmission delivers tactile engagement, coupled with a reinforced rear subframe to ensure structural rigidity under high lateral loads. The suspension geometry remains true, utilizing fresh bushings and OEM dampers for that signature M-chassis feedback. Finished in collector-quality condition with a documented service history, this is a turn-key analog icon for the discerning driver.",
